description:
Join me for a live stream to celebrate the birth of Christ, reflect on the Incarnation, and to sing my favorite Christmas songs!  It's a very atheist Christmas!  All my atheist friends are welcome!  And hopefully some Christians too!  Join the stream and share your thoughts about Christmas.  Be forewarned, I may burst out into song and expect you to sing along!

With appearances and songs:
@DigitalGnosis 
@DannyPhilTalk 
@mercyofGod432 
@EvidenceandReasons 

You can several Christmas songs produced by Bread of Life available on Spotify, iTunes, and other music services under "Bread of Life Music" EP, "Love in the Flesh." 

Here is the link on Spotify:
https://open.spotify.com/album/2POhUVIWows8mrgTG88ka1?si=P6tXo1gLSUCigQcJ0CuRJQ

I had the great privilege of attending the Capturing Christianity conference in Houston last weekend.  It was a wonderful event with amazing people.  Just wanted to invite others to share their thoughts on the conference.  Join the stream!

@CapturingChristianity 

On the stream:
@MaverickChristian 
@Wolves Do Apologetics 
@DannyPhilTalk 
@ApologeticsSquared 
@SentinelApologetics 
@shroudofturin-888 


For more videos on topics related to Christian faith, visit my website:
breadoflifechannel.net

